BELLOWP.name: Bell OWP
notes: You want to swap to :trait.slb.OPPRESSIVESUPERIORITY: with :novelty.bell: open before the fight starts, otherwise trait-swapping will remove your boons.

BRAWLER.name: Brawler Relic Precast
notes: Use :consumable.EQUIPTEMPLATE: keybinds to swap or swap :relic.brawler: from inventory.
You want to be merged :skill.slb.beastmode: before using :weapon.slb.s3: to apply protection on yourself to trigger the relic.

EXEAXE.name: Executioner Axe Entry
notes: You can enter into combat if you are not careful with the :weapon.slb.lb5: positioning.
Use :skill.slb.QUICKENINGZEPHYR: at the mistlock to give yourself enough superspeed before entering the fight.

CLAW.name: Claw Relic Precast
notes: Use :consumable.EQUIPTEMPLATE: keybinds to swap or swap :relic.claw: from inventory.
You can bind :novelty.chest: novelties to a keybind to open and use them.

PRETRAP.name: Trap Precast
notes: You will need to use a trap->dodge technique to be able to switch your traps back to normal utility skills.
